title: PLACE_OBJECT_ON_GROUND_OR_OBJECT_PROPERLY
content:
0xD76EEEF746057FD6// PlaceObjectOnGroundOrObjectProperly
BOOL PLACE_OBJECT_ON_GROUND_OR_OBJECT_PROPERLY(Object object);Parameters:object: The object handle.Casts a ray downward from the object's position and places the object on the surface it hits (including world surface and objects). Use PLACE_OBJECT_ON_GROUND_PROPERLY to not include objects when determining the surface.Old name:  _PLACE_OBJECT_ON_GROUND_PROPERLY_2
